28. tr - Convert file contents into uppercase , also learn "-s" option of this command
 cat select.txt | tr "a-z" "A-z"
ORANGE
MANGO
BANANA
GRAPE
WATERMELON

tr -s " " ","
hello mydestiny
hello,mydestiny
i hope you are the best that anyone can think of
i,hope,you,are,the,best,that,anyone,can,think,of
thank you 
thank,you,

