29. cut - Split the file contents using delimiter and print required fields

> ls -l | tr -s " " "$" |cut -d "$" -f3,4,5 | tr -s "$" " "

sunbeam sunbeam 1245069
sunbeam sunbeam 7479
sunbeam sunbeam 5110
sunbeam sunbeam 37
sunbeam sunbeam 4096



